# .qa-shared — list non-tracked files to mount read-only into QA containers
# Copy this file to your APP_ROOT as .qa-shared and uncomment what applies.
# Paths are relative to your project root (APP_ROOT).
# Lines starting with # are comments; blank lines are ignored.
#
# Common entries:
# d2r2-frontend/.env.local
# d2r2-frontend/.npmrc
# d2r2-backend/.env
# .env
